content: just noticed we have 5 open PRs on the std-dev-guide that have been falling through the cracks, so I'm going to setup highfive for that repo to make sure PRs get reviewed and landed consistently

maybe that should be done for blog.rust-lang.org too, for instance @Jubilee made a portable-simd announcement pull request that has been apparently ignored for 4mo: https://github.com/rust-lang/blog.rust-lang.org/pull/906
